Name: Paint Warfare
About the game: Paint Warfare is the fastest, wildest and most adrenaline-packed multiplayer FPS you’ll ever experience. With wall climbing, grenade jumping and hyper-fast movement, you can explore virtually any point in the maps. Key Points: Wacky movement— incredible speed, grenade jumping, dashes and wall climbing Every weapon is unique— from orange grenades to banana guns and shotgun pistols, every weapon is different Maps— although there are currently 3, many more are in the works :) Easy to play with friends— available on both itch.io and steam and friendly on beginners, the maps allow for anything from a simple duel to a massive paint brawl Paint Warfare— Play without limits
